                    <strong>Q1 2026 Sales Review.</strong> Over the last 6 months
                    across all regions, revenue reached
                    <strong>$6,572,100</strong> — 110% of the $6,000,000 target (on track).
                    <strong>North America</strong> led the period.
                    <div style="margin-top:8px;opacity:.75"><em>Analyst notes:</em> APAC expansion drove the quarter; watch Latin America pipeline.</div>
                  </div>
              metadata: {}
              execution_count: 13
          type: code
          content: >-
            import html


            best = view.groupby("region")["revenue_k"].sum().idxmax()

            on_track = "on track" if pct >= 100 else f"{100 - pct:.0f}% short"


            # Escape the free-text inputs before interpolating them into HTML.

            title = html.escape(str(report_title))

            notes = html.escape(str(analyst_notes))


            HTML(f'''

            <div style="font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;color:inherit;line-height:1.6;
                        border-left:3px solid #4a25c9;padding:2px 0 2px 14px">
              <strong>{title}.</strong> Over the last {months} months
              {('for ' + selected) if selected else 'across all regions'}, revenue reached
              <strong>${total:,.0f}</strong> — {pct:.0f}% of the ${target_total:,.0f} target ({on_track}).
              <strong>{best}</strong> led the period.
              <div style="margin-top:8px;opacity:.75"><em>Analyst notes:</em> {notes}</div>
            </div>

            ''')
          metadata: {}
        - id: c00000000000000000000000000a0001
          blockGroup: a0000000-0000-4000-8000-00000000a001
          sortingKey: "000015"
          type: text-cell-h2
          content: Agentic analysis
          metadata: {}
        - id: c00000000000000000000000000a0002
          blockGroup: a0000000-0000-4000-8000-00000000a002
          sortingKey: "000016"
          outputs:
            - output_type: stream
              name: stdout
              text: >
                Executive readout — Q1 2026 Sales Review


                Revenue over the last six months reached $6,572,100 — 110% of the $6.0M target and

                up 13.7% versus the prior six months. The beat is broad-based: the monthly trend held

                at or above the per-month target across most of the window rather than riding a single

                strong month.


                What drove it

                - North America remains the largest contributor by absolute revenue and anchored the period.

                - Asia Pacific is the fastest-growing region (~3%/month) and is the main reason the blended
                  growth rate reached double digits; on its current trajectory it overtakes Europe within a
                  couple of quarters.

                Risk

                - Latin America is the smallest region and grows slowest. It adds little to the beat today, so
                  any pipeline softness there pulls down next period’s growth rate more than its size suggests.

                Recommendation

                - Re-weight Q2 quota and demand-gen spend toward Asia Pacific to bank its momentum, while
                  funding a focused pipeline-recovery play in Latin America to keep the blended rate above target.
          type: agent
          content: "You are a senior revenue analyst. Using the dashboard above — revenue by region, the monthly trend versus
            target, and the analyst notes — write a concise executive readout: the headline number and how it compares
            to target, what drove it, the main risk, and one recommendation."
          metadata:
            deepnote_agent_model: gpt-5
      executionMode: block
      id: 9b1f7c00-0000-4a00-9000-locrunnernb001
      name: Dashboard
